R. Kelly is due to appear in a Chicago court, Tuesday on charges of recruiting girls and women to have illegal sex with him. Prosecutors say Kelly should not make bail and want him to remain in federal custody as they say he's a flight risk.  The 52 year old R&B star, is also accused of covering up the crimes by paying and threatening the victims and witnesses. The musician is also awaiting trial for more than 20 other alleged sexual crimes, all of which he denies.